00:03:33.903 --> 00:03:34.463
Su Majestad,

00:03:35.143 --> 00:03:36.343
Ella es el demonio.

00:03:36.703 --> 00:03:37.543
Mátala.

00:03:38.023 --> 00:03:38.823
¡No!

00:03:40.823 --> 00:03:41.663
Su Majestad.

00:03:41.983 --> 00:03:44.503
